             were indicted for <rs id="t18311020-17-off96" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18311020-17-off96" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311020-17-off96" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18311020-17-cd97" type="crimeDate">12th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-17-off96 t18311020-17-cd97"></join>, 1 rule, value 1s., and 1 handkerchief, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18311020-17-victim245" type="victimName">
                  Joseph 
                  Lacey
               <interp inst="t18311020-17-victim245" type="surname" value="Lacey"></interp>
